        "start": 35,
        "end": 37
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_021_000165",
    "sentence": "二年，庶人友珪篡位，加檢校司徒。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "二年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 2
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_021_000166",
    "sentence": "三年正月，授濮州刺史、本州馬步軍都指揮使，依前左先鋒馬軍使。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "三年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 2
      },
      {
        "text": "授濮州",
